522
00:46:29,200 --> 00:46:30,360
I…

523
00:46:36,440 --> 00:46:37,600
I don't know.

524
00:46:42,520 --> 00:46:44,040
But I do believe

525
00:46:45,680 --> 00:46:47,880
you can handle this.

526
00:46:52,960 --> 00:46:55,400
You don't need to be scared over nothing.

527
00:46:57,800 --> 00:47:00,400
No one really cares about that family.

528
00:47:02,200 --> 00:47:04,920
<i>People only get excited</i>
<i>because it's trending.</i>

529
00:47:05,000 --> 00:47:09,400
<i>There are much bigger cases than this</i>
<i>that never get solved.</i>

530
00:47:09,480 --> 00:47:11,760
A normal family like that…

531
00:47:14,000 --> 00:47:15,560
People will forget them soon enough.

532
00:47:20,320 --> 00:47:23,040
I think we should stop
talking about stressful things.

533
00:47:24,240 --> 00:47:26,080
Let me help you relax instead.

534
00:48:17,200 --> 00:48:18,040
Whoa.

535
00:48:19,360 --> 00:48:22,520
Our contact said they found
nothing suspicious on Fahsai's side.

536
00:48:23,600 --> 00:48:25,080
We followed her for nothing.

537
00:48:27,000 --> 00:48:28,040
It's fine.

538
00:48:29,080 --> 00:48:31,920
At this point, Samut's already
under enough scrutiny from the public.

539
00:48:32,000 --> 00:48:35,280
I thought we were going to get
some new lead or something.

540
00:48:41,080 --> 00:48:43,880
He's coming.

541
00:48:43,960 --> 00:48:46,040
Mr. Mahasamut, may we have an interview?

542
00:48:46,800 --> 00:48:49,640
After being implicated
by the Mad Dog online news page,

543
00:48:49,720 --> 00:48:53,240
will this affect the upcoming election?

544
00:48:54,720 --> 00:48:57,280
I've already filed a lawsuit in response.

545
00:48:58,440 --> 00:49:03,120
Even an online news outlet
should have ethics in reporting.

546
00:49:04,400 --> 00:49:07,680
And I believe society will know
the truth very soon. Excuse me.

547
00:49:07,760 --> 00:49:09,560
But people are saying

548
00:49:09,640 --> 00:49:12,240
that every politician targeted by Mad Dog

549
00:49:12,320 --> 00:49:17,360
ends up having
their political career destroyed.

550
00:49:17,440 --> 00:49:20,720
If Mad Dog is so sure of themselves,

551
00:49:21,360 --> 00:49:23,560
then they should
come forward with evidence.

552
00:49:25,040 --> 00:49:26,240
If they don't have any,

553
00:49:27,080 --> 00:49:29,560
then they're the ones
whose job should be over.

554
00:49:30,960 --> 00:49:33,800
So this is basically
a challenge to Mad Dog?

555
00:49:33,880 --> 00:49:36,200
You sound very confident, Mr. Mahasamut.

556
00:49:50,080 --> 00:49:52,760
Boss, the comments on your interview

557
00:49:52,840 --> 00:49:56,000
are mostly siding with Mad Dog.

558
00:49:56,520 --> 00:49:59,720
That they must have some evidence.
Will this be a problem?

559
00:50:00,800 --> 00:50:02,600
I think your scandal

560
00:50:03,280 --> 00:50:05,320
is going to ruin my project.

561
00:50:05,920 --> 00:50:08,960
The minister won't take my calls anymore,
won't meet with me.

562
00:50:09,040 --> 00:50:10,320
We're getting abandoned.

563
00:50:15,760 --> 00:50:18,480
Won't you do anything other than sue them?

564
00:50:19,560 --> 00:50:21,480
You know how much I had to pay.

565
00:50:21,560 --> 00:50:24,680
And if this project slips away,
then what do we do?

566
00:50:29,640 --> 00:50:30,880
I already told you

567
00:50:32,240 --> 00:50:35,240
there's no problem,
then there's no problem.

568
00:50:36,800 --> 00:50:38,160
I hope that's true.

569
00:50:39,120 --> 00:50:42,920
I'll try contacting
the minister again tomorrow.

570
00:51:09,800 --> 00:51:12,120
Hey! Hey!

571
00:51:12,200 --> 00:51:13,960
Hey!

572
00:51:14,040 --> 00:51:15,560
Why are you hiding behind my back?

573
00:51:15,640 --> 00:51:18,840
Don't shoot. Please don't shoot.
Please spare me.

574
00:51:23,320 --> 00:51:25,840
Hey!

575
00:51:29,800 --> 00:51:31,440
- Come here.
- Don’t struggle!

576
00:51:33,120 --> 00:51:34,280
Are you alright?

577
00:51:34,360 --> 00:51:36,600
- Thank you, boss. I'm fine.
- You're safe, sir.

578
00:51:36,680 --> 00:51:37,560
- You're safe.
- Sure?

579
00:51:37,640 --> 00:51:38,640
Yes.

580
00:51:49,760 --> 00:51:52,920
<i>Gunmen brazenly attacked</i>
<i>a major contractor last night.</i>

581
00:51:53,000 --> 00:51:55,600
<i>Guards from Heaven Club came out to help.</i>

582
00:51:55,680 --> 00:52:00,680
<i>As seen in the clip, the gunman was about</i>
<i>to shoot a female staff member,</i>

583
00:52:00,760 --> 00:52:05,480
<i>but the man who stopped the gunman</i>
<i>and saved her was this man right here.</i>

584
00:52:07,720 --> 00:52:10,120
Hey. He looks insanely cool.

585
00:52:10,720 --> 00:52:13,160
But isn't this the same guy
the Mad Dog page just hinted

586
00:52:13,240 --> 00:52:16,120
was involved in that med student
family murder case?

587
00:52:16,200 --> 00:52:18,040
Really? I had no idea.

588
00:52:18,120 --> 00:52:20,400
That story was huge.
How could you not know?

589
00:52:20,480 --> 00:52:23,120
Well, judging from
how he helped that woman,

590
00:52:23,200 --> 00:52:24,440
he seems like a good person.

591
00:52:24,520 --> 00:52:26,280
No bad person
would help someone like that.

592
00:52:26,360 --> 00:52:27,800
A good person is a good person.

593
00:52:27,880 --> 00:52:29,160
Right.

594
00:52:30,680 --> 00:52:31,640
You like him, don't you?

595
00:52:31,720 --> 00:52:35,040
Of course I do.
He's handsome and seems nice too.

596
00:52:35,120 --> 00:52:38,160
How many times
have you watched that clip today?

597
00:52:38,240 --> 00:52:42,200
I seriously can't move on.
I've never seen a politician this hot.

598
00:52:45,600 --> 00:52:47,000
Please don't be upset with me.

599
00:52:47,080 --> 00:52:49,680
I didn't speak very well to you
last night.

600
00:52:58,400 --> 00:53:02,840
I really have to thank you. Otherwise,
I wouldn't even be alive right now.

601
00:53:02,920 --> 00:53:04,280
It was nothing.

602
00:53:08,040 --> 00:53:09,360
As for the minister,

603
00:53:10,800 --> 00:53:16,120
I heard he was busy yesterday,
so he couldn't get back to you.

604
00:53:16,840 --> 00:53:18,760
Today his secretary
is supposed to call, right?

605
00:53:18,840 --> 00:53:22,160
Yes. I got the message.
The meeting's been arranged.

606
00:53:24,800 --> 00:53:27,400
I don't even know how to thank you.

607
00:53:28,320 --> 00:53:30,800
You're my hero.

608
00:53:30,880 --> 00:53:33,320
I really picked the right person.

609
00:53:36,840 --> 00:53:38,680
It's not that dramatic.

610
00:53:40,160 --> 00:53:41,360
I just

611
00:53:43,440 --> 00:53:47,040
believe that anyone who works with me
should be taken care of properly.

612
00:53:48,920 --> 00:53:50,440
As for what happened before,

613
00:53:52,560 --> 00:53:53,520
I'm not holding it against you.

614
00:54:11,960 --> 00:54:12,840
Boss,

615
00:54:14,120 --> 00:54:17,360
the female staff member has already given
her statement about you saving her.

616
00:54:17,960 --> 00:54:20,000
And the gunmen?

617
00:54:20,080 --> 00:54:21,280
I took care of it.

618
00:54:22,600 --> 00:54:24,360
They won't dare betray us.

619
00:54:24,440 --> 00:54:25,360
Besides,

620
00:54:26,120 --> 00:54:27,760
I already paid them to keep quiet,

621
00:54:28,400 --> 00:54:29,840
so there's nothing to worry about.

622
00:54:39,000 --> 00:54:40,680
He actually saved that contractor

623
00:54:40,760 --> 00:54:42,760
and spun the story
into him saving a woman instead.

624
00:54:42,840 --> 00:54:46,000
So? That's your handsome guy.
Have you seen his true colors yet?

625
00:54:47,520 --> 00:54:48,680
But…

626
00:54:49,200 --> 00:54:51,640
Pulling off a turnaround like that
is still kind of hot.

627
00:54:52,440 --> 00:54:53,880
Oh, come on.

628
00:54:53,960 --> 00:54:56,280
If you talk like that,
this isn't Mad Dog anymore.

629
00:54:57,840 --> 00:54:59,360
We had him cornered.

630
00:55:00,320 --> 00:55:01,400
What a waste.

631
00:55:04,200 --> 00:55:05,800
He only knows how to create an image.

632
00:55:06,600 --> 00:55:08,600
None of the evil he's done
has gone anywhere.

633
00:55:09,560 --> 00:55:11,880
We're going to rip off his mask
before the election.

634
00:55:15,160 --> 00:55:16,240
This area here

635
00:55:18,240 --> 00:55:22,160
is a suspected hideout
according to our intelligence unit.

636
00:55:24,240 --> 00:55:27,200
Really, Captain?
That's right in the middle of the city.

637
00:55:27,920 --> 00:55:30,800
Our sources reported
seeing injured suspects

638
00:55:30,880 --> 00:55:32,600
taken into that neighborhood.

639
00:55:32,680 --> 00:55:33,840
But when they came back out,

640
00:55:33,920 --> 00:55:36,120
they'd been treated professionally.

641
00:55:36,200 --> 00:55:38,720
Some of them were shot
so badly they should've died,

642
00:55:38,800 --> 00:55:40,000
but they somehow survived.

643
00:55:43,640 --> 00:55:46,680
Captain, someone transported
a suspect with a gunshot wound

644
00:55:46,760 --> 00:55:48,000
into the suspect area.

645
00:55:48,080 --> 00:55:49,480
- Right now?
- Yes, sir.

646
00:55:52,040 --> 00:55:54,400
Black Doc’s gang won’t get away this time.

647
00:55:55,040 --> 00:55:57,320
- Let's go! Now!
- Let's go.

648
00:57:02,400 --> 00:57:04,040
Call in backup to the target point.

649
00:57:50,040 --> 00:57:50,960
He's down there!

650
00:58:35,920 --> 00:58:38,880
- Oh! Officer.
- Yes?

651
00:58:39,680 --> 00:58:40,520
You can't come in.

652
00:58:40,600 --> 00:58:42,240
I'm chasing a suspect.

653
00:58:42,320 --> 00:58:44,200
Your shoes may carry germs.

654
00:58:44,280 --> 00:58:46,880
They could make the animals sick.
Please come in through the front.

655
00:58:53,480 --> 00:58:54,400
Excuse me.

656
00:58:56,120 --> 00:58:57,040
Hey.

657
00:59:00,600 --> 00:59:02,440
Did you bring police dogs here
for treatment?

658
00:59:02,520 --> 00:59:05,040
No, Well, you're…

659
00:59:05,120 --> 00:59:08,880
Prapai. I'm a vet here.
And I'm also the owner.

660
00:59:09,480 --> 00:59:13,240
Yes, Doctor. I suspect a criminal
may be hiding in here.

661
00:59:13,320 --> 00:59:14,720
- So I'd like to ask for…
- To search?

662
00:59:18,800 --> 00:59:20,880
Let's call it requesting your cooperation.

663
00:59:28,720 --> 00:59:30,040
This is the last area.

664
00:59:31,000 --> 00:59:34,800
Honestly, I doubt a criminal
would hide in my hospital.

665
00:59:35,640 --> 00:59:36,880
If there were someone in here,

666
00:59:37,480 --> 00:59:39,120
all the dogs and cats

667
00:59:39,200 --> 00:59:40,760
would already be making a huge fuss.

668
00:59:45,720 --> 00:59:46,560
Right?

669
00:59:49,400 --> 00:59:51,680
But I'd still like to check,
just to be sure.

670
00:59:52,280 --> 00:59:53,760
Of course. But…

671
00:59:55,320 --> 00:59:58,000
You need to hurry a little.
I've got to examine an iguana next.

672
00:59:58,080 --> 00:59:59,320
I'd like to check this room.

673
01:00:00,760 --> 01:00:02,200
It's only a storage room.

674
01:00:08,000 --> 01:00:09,680
Permission to search.

675
01:00:12,600 --> 01:00:13,640
Go ahead.

676
01:00:48,960 --> 01:00:51,600
<i>Are you saying Mr. Wayu,</i>
<i>the owner of this house, is a stalker?</i>

677
01:00:51,680 --> 01:00:54,360
I should be thanking Mr. Wayu

678
01:00:54,440 --> 01:00:57,040
for risking himself to save me.

679
01:00:57,560 --> 01:00:59,120
Should I invite him out to thank him?

680
01:00:59,200 --> 01:01:03,200
Mr. Mahasamut wants to meet me
and thank me?

681
01:01:09,360 --> 01:01:10,360
Mr. Wayu.

682
01:01:10,440 --> 01:01:11,920
Are you sure it's really just dinner?

683
01:01:12,000 --> 01:01:13,120
Lena,

684
01:01:13,200 --> 01:01:15,480
how long have you worked with me already?

685
01:01:15,560 --> 01:01:16,640
I'd like to clarify this.

686
01:01:16,720 --> 01:01:17,560
What is this clip?

687
01:01:17,640 --> 01:01:19,120
It shows

688
01:01:19,200 --> 01:01:22,040
your car and Lena's van
entering the same resort.

689
01:01:22,120 --> 01:01:24,680
Did you arrange for Lena
to take on hostess work?

690
01:01:24,760 --> 01:01:26,080
What's happening out there?

691
01:01:26,840 --> 01:01:29,600
There's an audio clip
the Mad Dog page just released.

692
01:01:29,680 --> 01:01:32,400
<i>As for that Mad Dog page</i>
<i>exposing the Peeraka case,</i>

693
01:01:32,480 --> 01:01:33,960
<i>set him up.</i>

694
01:02:33,000 --> 01:02:34,720
Subtitle translation by: Panuwat Baikeawon
